title: Stars who channel other Hollywood icons
text: Blogs Stars who channel other Hollywood icons Would you check out these sexy copycats? Whether it's for a photo shoot or a movie role, the stars love to dress up as each other and cultural icons. See which famous impersonations have us doing double takes ... Photo: AXELLE WOUSSEN/Bauergriffin.com, LucasFilm.Ltd./ Published: 10/5/2015 12:43:17 Kaley Cuoco as Luke Skywalker It looks like Kaley Cuoco knows how to put on quite the show! During the 2nd Annual Longines Masters of Los Angeles horse jumping event, the actress stepped out in a Jedi costume looking much like Luke Skywalker on Oct. 3, 2015. 1 of 22
